.Dd $Mdocdate$
.Dt C_NIX_MKPATH 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm c_nix_mkpath
.Nd create directory path
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb tertium
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In tertium/cpu.h
.In tertium/std.h
.Ft ctype_status
.Fn c_nix_mkpath "char *dir" "uint dmode" "uint mode"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn c_nix_mkpath
function creates the directory
.Fa dir  ,
creating any missing parent directories with the permissions set to
.Fa dmode ,
and set its permissions to
.Fa mode .
.Sh RETURN VALUES
.Rv -std
.Sh ERRORS
The
.Fn c_nix_mkpath
function may fail and set the external variable
.Va errno
for any of the errors specified for the library function
.Xr c_nix_mkdir 3 .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr c_nix_mkdir 3 ,
.Xr c_nix_rmpath
